'''2016年布鲁塞尔连环爆炸案'''是指2016年3月22日在[[比利时|比利时]]首都[[布鲁塞尔|布鲁塞尔]]及周边地区发生的连环爆炸[[恐怖袭击|恐怖袭击]]事件，[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]在事發後宣布對此事負責。

当日8:00在[[布鲁塞尔机场|布鲁塞尔机场]]发生两次爆炸，随后9:11在[[欧盟|欧盟]]多个部门总部附近的{{link-nl|馬爾貝克站|Maalbeek (metrostation)|馬爾貝克地鐵站}}<ref name="rthk20150322"/>发生了第三次爆炸袭击，共造成32名受害者死亡，此外3名自殺炸彈客亦在爆炸中死亡，至少340人受傷。<ref name="Yahoo0330toll">{{cite news|url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/belgium-resumes-hunt-airport-suspect-criticism-mounts-004723635.html|title=Brussels airport delays reopening as Belgium lowers attacks toll to 32|work=Yahoo|date=2016-03-30|accessdate=2016-03-30|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408180906/https://www.yahoo.com/news/belgium-resumes-hunt-airport-suspect-criticism-mounts-004723635.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN Mar26">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/26/europe/brussels-investigation-main/|title=Investigators hunt more suspects after Brussels terror attacks|work=CNN|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328014314/http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/26/europe/brussels-investigation-main/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Guardian Mar26">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/26/man-charged-brussels-terror-attacks-faycal-c-belgian-barack-obama|title=Fayçal Cheffou charged over core role in Brussels bomb attacks|work=Guardian|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326201500/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/26/man-charged-brussels-terror-attacks-faycal-c-belgian-barack-obama|dead-url=no}}</ref>这次连环爆炸案是比利时历史上最严重的恐怖袭击。<ref name="Bloomberg">{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-03-22/belgium-s-worst-terror-attack-ever-leaves-31-dead-in-brussels|title=Belgium Hunts Jihadists That Struck Heart of a Fraying Europe|work=Bloomberg|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323113637/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-03-22/belgium-s-worst-terror-attack-ever-leaves-31-dead-in-brussels|dead-url=no}}</ref>政府隨後宣布哀悼三天。

== 背景 ==
比利时积极参与了[[对伊斯兰国的军事干预|对伊斯兰国的多国联合军事干预]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/world-news/iraq-danes-send-attack-planes-30619237.html|title=Iraq: Danes send attack planes|last=Morris|first=Nigel|date=2014-09-27|work=Belfast Telegraph|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404185045/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/news/world-news/iraq-danes-send-attack-planes-30619237.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该国人口中亦有大量人员成为伊斯兰国的外国武装分子。截至2015年1月估计有440人逃往叙利亚和伊拉克，占国家总人口的比例是在西欧诸国中最高的。<ref name="cnn hotbed">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/21/europe/belgium-terror-fight-molenbeek/|title=Belgium: Europe's front line in the war on terror|author=Nina Elbagir|author2=Bharati Nailk|author3=Laila Ben Allal|date=2016-03-22|work=CNN|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403213845/http://www.edition.cnn.com/2016/03/21/europe/belgium-terror-fight-molenbeek/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Neumann">{{cite web|last1=Neumann|first1=Peter|title=Foreign fighter total in Syria/Iraq now exceeds 20,000; surpasses Afghanistan conflict in the 1980s|url=http://icsr.info/2015/01/foreign-fighter-total-syriairaq-now-exceeds-20000-surpasses-afghanistan-conflict-1980s/|publisher=ICSR|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329074323/http://icsr.info/2015/01/foreign-fighter-total-syriairaq-now-exceeds-20000-surpasses-afghanistan-conflict-1980s/|dead-url=no}}</ref>比利时也因此被称为“[[圣战|圣战分子]]意识形态的温床”<ref name="cnn hotbed" />和“圣战分子招募中心”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/how-belgium-became-a-jihadist-recruiting-hub-1411958283|title=How Belgium Became a Jihadist-Recruiting Hub|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404113541/http://www.wsj.com/articles/how-belgium-became-a-jihadist-recruiting-hub-1411958283|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

事发前的数起伊斯兰恐怖袭击事件都发源于比利时，该国亦多次发起反恐行动。2014年5月，一名跟[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]有关联的枪手袭击了布鲁塞尔{{le|比利时犹太博物馆|Jewish Museum of Belgium}}，造成{{le|比利时犹太博物馆枪击案|Jewish Museum of Belgium shooting|四人死亡}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lesoir.be/559864/article/actualite/belgique/2014-06-01/fusillade-au-musee-juif-bruxelles-un-francais-arrete|accessdate=2014-06-06|publisher=Le Soir|date=2014-06-01|title=Fusillade au Musée juif de Bruxelles: un Français arrêté|archive-date=2014-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604201419/http://www.lesoir.be/559864/article/actualite/belgique/2014-06-01/fusillade-au-musee-juif-bruxelles-un-francais-arrete|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="fourthvictim">{{cite news|url=http://www.demorgen.be/dm/nl/30966/Schietpartij-aan-Joods-Museum-in-Brussel/article/detail/1910854/2014/06/06/Vierde-slachtoffer-aanslag-Joods-museum-overleden.dhtml|title=Vierde slachtoffer aanslag Joods museum overleden|date=2014-06-06|publisher=De Morgen|accessdate=2014-06-06|archive-date=2014-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728223443/http://www.demorgen.be/dm/nl/30966/Schietpartij-aan-Joods-Museum-in-Brussel/article/detail/1910854/2014/06/06/Vierde-slachtoffer-aanslag-Joods-museum-overleden.dhtml|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="BBC suspect">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27654505|title=Brussels Jewish Museum killings: Man held in Marseille|date=2014-06-01|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2014-06-01|archive-date=2018-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180104195857/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-27654505|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月，比利时发起反恐行动，端掉一个策划在布鲁塞尔和[[扎芬特姆|扎芬特姆]]制造第二起[[查理周刊总部枪击案|查理周刊总部枪击案]]的团伙<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30840160|title=Belgian anti-terror raid in Verviers 'leaves two dead'|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-01-15|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828014359/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-30840160|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CBC">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/belgian-counterterrorism-raid-in-verviers-leaves-2-dead-report-says-1.2902052|title=Belgian counterterrorism raid in Verviers leaves 2 dead, report says|publisher=CBC News|date=2015-01-15|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403084656/https://www.cbc.ca/news/world/belgian-counterterrorism-raid-in-verviers-leaves-2-dead-report-says-1.2902052|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年8月，一名可疑的恐怖分子登上一辆从[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]途径布鲁塞尔前往[[巴黎|巴黎]]的[[大力士高速列车|大力士高速列车]]上意图[[大力士高速列車槍擊案|发动袭击]]，最后被乘客制服<ref name="BBC34023361">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34023361|title=France train shooting: Three hurt and man arrested|publisher=BBC News|date=2015-08-22|accessdate=2015-08-21|archive-date=2019-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190817032219/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34023361|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

近年来，布鲁塞尔的[[莫伦贝克-圣让|莫伦贝克地区]]逐渐成为圣战主义者和极端主义者聚居的地区，被称作“欧洲的圣战中心”。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/15/molenbeek-the-brussels-borough-in-the-spotlight-after-paris-attacks|title=Molenbeek: the Brussels borough becoming known as Europe's jihadi central|work=The Guardian|date=2015-11-15|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323184251/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/nov/15/molenbeek-the-brussels-borough-in-the-spotlight-after-paris-attacks|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年11月巴黎袭击事件]]的参与者就以此为大本营，该市也曾全城封锁五天，以方便警察搜寻犯罪嫌疑人。2016年3月18日，巴黎袭击案的共犯{{le|萨拉赫·阿卜杜勒－萨拉姆|Salah Abdeslam}}在反恐行动中被抓获，该次行动击毙了另一名嫌犯，另有两人受伤。至少有一名嫌犯仍在逃<ref>{{cite news|date=2016-03-15|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/15/europe/brussels-paris-attacks-shots-fired/index.html|title=Shots in Brussels raid tied to Paris attacks|work=CNN|accessdate=2016-03-15|archive-date=2019-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405100204/https://www.cnn.com/2016/03/15/europe/brussels-paris-attacks-shots-fired/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|date=2016-03-15|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-35809974|title=Gunfire in Brussels raid on 'Paris attacks suspects'|work=BBC News|accessdate=2016-03-15|archive-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828014530/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-35809974|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rt">{{cite web|title=Paris attacks suspect Salah Abdeslam shot, arrested in Brussels raid|url=https://www.rt.com/news/336137-brussels-police-raid-shots/|publisher=Russia Today|date=2016-03-18|accessdate=2016-03-18|archive-date=2019-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512125240/https://www.rt.com/news/336137-brussels-police-raid-shots/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35860157|title=Paris attacks: Salah Abdeslam 'worth his weight in gold'|work=BBC News|date=2016-03-21|accessdate=2016-03-21|archive-date=2019-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825024739/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35860157|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比利时调查人员认为，这一爆炸案可能是伊斯兰国对阿卜杜勒－萨拉姆被捕一事的报复行动。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/terror-arrest-belgium-accelerated-timetable-brussels-bombings-us/story?id=37852983|title=Terror Arrest In Belgium Likely Accelerated Timetable for Brussels Bombings, US Lawmakers Say|work=ABC News|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|author=Benjamin Siegel|author2=Alexander Mallin|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323052226/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/terror-arrest-belgium-accelerated-timetable-brussels-bombings-us/story?id=37852983|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="telegragh revenge">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12200965/Brussels-explosions-who-are-the-likely-terror-suspects-behind-the-attack.html|title=Brussels explosions: who are the likely terror suspects behind the attack?|work=The Telegraph|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322120144/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12200965/Brussels-explosions-who-are-the-likely-terror-suspects-behind-the-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/22/brussels-attacks-show-how-global-terror-networks-act-local|title=Brussels attack: were they revenge for Abdeslam's arrest?|work=The Guardian|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322094411/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/mar/22/brussels-attacks-show-how-global-terror-networks-act-local|dead-url=no}}</ref>比利时内政部长{{le|扬·让邦|Jan Jambon}}在案发后表示当局在事前已经预想到可能会有更多袭击发生，但远远低估了袭击的规模。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/brussels-attacks-isis-claims-responsibility-deadly-bombings-airport-subway/|title=Brussels attacks: Photo, wanted notice released for suspect|work=CBS|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323185337/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/brussels-attacks-isis-claims-responsibility-deadly-bombings-airport-subway/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

