=== 布鲁塞尔机场 ===
3月22日早上8时，[[比利时|比利时]][[布鲁塞尔机场|布鲁塞尔机场]]发生间隔37秒的两次爆炸，爆炸都发生在国际出发大厅的值机区域。<ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/><ref name="BBCsofar">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35869985|title=Brussels explosions: What we know about airport and metro attacks|work=BBC|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331232803/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35869985|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩次爆炸还導致11人死亡。<ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/><ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12200780/Brussels-airport-explosions-Reports-of-two-blasts-as-smoke-rises-from-terminal-building.html|title=Brussels Zaventem airport explosions: 'At least 11 dead' and multiple injuries as two blasts rock terminal building - latest|work=Telegraph|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322081018/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12200780/Brussels-airport-explosions-Reports-of-two-blasts-as-smoke-rises-from-terminal-building.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBClive22Mar16">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-europe-35869266|title=Brussels blasts: BBC TV coverage|work=BBC|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322085057/http://www.bbc.com/news/live/world-europe-35869266|dead-url=no}}</ref>爆炸还造成主航站楼窗户破碎，航站楼内部也有严重损坏。<ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/news/336519-explosions-hit-brussels-airport/|title=Explosion at Brussels Airport took place near American Airlines desk - reports|work=RT International|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2018-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180120182054/https://www.rt.com/news/336519-explosions-hit-brussels-airport/|dead-url=no}}</ref>比利时官方证实称爆炸为自杀性袭击。此外还有报道称爆炸前机场内有枪声和[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]的喊叫声。<ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBC initial report" /><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/people-injured-after-explosion-at-brussels-airport-police-say-1458632527|title=Brussels Rocked by Terrorist Attacks, Killing at Least 27 People|work=Wall Street Journal|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322100330/http://www.wsj.com/articles/people-injured-after-explosion-at-brussels-airport-police-say-1458632527|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方之后在袭击者尸体旁发现了一把[[AK-47突击步枪|AK-47突击步枪]]，<ref name="chinadaily0322">{{cite news|url=http://world.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-03/22/content_24025732.htm|title=布鲁塞尔爆炸案两名嫌犯被捕 现场寻获一AK-47步枪|work=中国日报网|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-24|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325061424/http://world.chinadaily.com.cn/2016-03/22/content_24025732.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>还在机场附近发现了一枚未爆炸的炸弹，其威力强于已爆炸的两枚。随后专业人员通过可控爆炸排除了炸弹。<ref name="BBCsofar"/><ref name="BBClive22Mar16"/>

=== 馬爾貝克地铁站 ===
在布鲁塞尔机场爆炸发生之后，位于布鲁塞尔欧盟总部附近的{{link-en|馬爾貝克站|Maelbeek/Maalbeek metro station|馬爾貝克地鐵站}}<ref name="rthk20150322"/>在9:11左右发生了第三次爆炸。爆炸时列车正在驶离站台，炸弹位于三节车厢中的中间一节，当时尚未完全驶离站台范围。爆炸发生后，驾驶员立刻停车并疏散了前后两节车厢的乘客。<ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBCsofar"/>布鲁塞尔地铁运营部门确认地铁站的这次爆炸已造成20人死亡。<ref name="la libre">{{cite web |url=http://www.lalibre.be/actu/belgique/explosions-au-metro-de-maelbeek-une-situation-extremement-chaotique-photos-videos-56f1006a35702a22d59d46da |title=Explosions au métro de Maelbeek: une situation "extrêmement chaotique" |publisher=La Libre |date=2016年3月22日 |language=fr |accessdate=2016年3月22日 |archive-date=2016年3月25日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325003714/http://www.lalibre.be/actu/belgique/explosions-au-metro-de-maelbeek-une-situation-extremement-chaotique-photos-videos-56f1006a35702a22d59d46da |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="la libre"/><ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="rtbf">{{cite web|url=http://www.rtbf.be/info/belgique/detail_explosions-a-zaventem-et-dans-le-metro-bruxellois-le-pays-passe-en-niveau-4-de-la-menace?id=9247724|title=Attentat suicide à Zaventem confirmé, explosion à Maelbeek: respectivement 11 et 15 morts|date=2016-03-22|language=fr|accessdate=2016-03-22|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181436/https://www.rtbf.be/info/belgique/detail_explosions-a-zaventem-et-dans-le-metro-bruxellois-le-pays-passe-en-niveau-4-de-la-menace?id=9247724|dead-url=no}}</ref>

