3名自殺炸彈客引發的三次爆炸共造成32名平民遇難，其中四人是在院中死亡，至少340人受伤，其中61人情况危急。<ref name="Yahoo0330toll"/><ref name="Guardian Mar26"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35888271|title=Brussels attacks: Scores remain critical after bombings|work=BBC|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2016-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325065504/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35888271|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN victim">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/23/europe/brussels-attacks-victim-mourning-grief/index.html|title=Brussels attacks: Victims ID'd, loved ones sought|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2016-03-25|work=CNN|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325000012/http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/23/europe/brussels-attacks-victim-mourning-grief/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这是比利时历史上伤亡最惨重的一次恐怖袭击。<ref name="Bloomberg"/>伤亡人员中预计有超过40个国家的国民，因此身份识别的工作进行缓慢。<ref name="CNN victim"/>

== 嫌疑人 ==
[[File:Brussels_suspects_CCTV.jpg|thumb]]
警方共确认有至少五名嫌疑人参与了袭击。其中三人参与了机场的袭击，两人参与了地铁站的袭击。袭击者中有三名身份已确定，且在袭击中身亡；另有二人身份不明，其中一人在逃，一人状况不明。<ref name="CNN 6detained"/>

爆炸当天下午，警方根据机场监控视频确定了三名嫌疑人，并据此展开调查。机场监控视频中看到三人推着行李前行，其中便可能装有炸弹。两人左手戴黑色手套，其中可能藏有炸弹引爆装置。调查显示三人乘出租车前往机场，出租车司机向警方表示三人曾拒绝自己帮忙提行李。<ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/brussels-suicide-bombers-wore-one-glove-on-the-left-hand-2016-3|title=This detail about how the suspected Brussels suicide bombers wore their gloves might have been a giveaway|work=Business Insider|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325151926/http://uk.businessinsider.com/brussels-suicide-bombers-wore-one-glove-on-the-left-hand-2016-3|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="telegraph suspects">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12201359/Brussels-explosions-Police-release-image-of-b-mb-suspects.html|title=Police release image of Brussels bomb suspects wearing black glove on their left hand|work=Telegragh|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912100809/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12201359/Brussels-explosions-Police-release-image-of-bomb-suspects.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>次日，警方确定全部三起爆炸案中的两个自杀性袭击者的身份为1989年出生的哈立德·埃爾－巴克拉伊（{{lang|en|Khalid el-Bakraoui}}）和1986年出生的易卜拉欣·埃爾－巴克拉伊（{{lang|en|Ibrahim el-Bakraoui}}）{{noteTag|1=最初有媒体报道其姓名为卜拉欣·埃爾－巴克拉伊（{{lang|en|Brahim el-Bakraoui}}）。二人的姓氏亦有报道写作“埃爾·巴克拉伊”（{{lang|en|El Bakraoui}}）<ref name="nyt brothers"/>}}兄弟。二人都出生在比利时。<ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref name="CNN 6detained"/><ref name="nyt brothers">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/24/world/europe/brussels-attack.html|title=Brothers Among 3 Brussels Suicide Attackers; Another Assailant Is Sought|work=New York Times|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-24|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323172357/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/24/world/europe/brussels-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>机场监控画面中间者是易卜拉欣，他在机场实施了自杀袭击；而警方通过DNA检测证实证实哈立德在马尔贝克站引爆了身上的炸弹。<ref name="telegraph whois"/><ref name="BBClive22Mar16"/>哈立德此前已有前科，但此次是警方首次将这兄弟二人与恐怖主义活动联系起来。爆炸后数小时，警方根据出租车司机提供的线索搜查了哈立德以假名租住的公寓，在房间内发现了[[伊斯兰国国旗|伊斯兰国旗帜]]、突击步枪、[[雷管|雷管]]和15公斤的[[三過氧化三丙酮|TATP]]炸药等炸弹制备材料，以及[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年巴黎袭击案]]主要嫌疑人{{le|萨拉赫·阿卜杜勒－萨拉姆|Salah Abdeslam}}的指纹，怀疑这二人与巴黎恐袭亦有关联。<ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-khalid-brahim-el-bakraoui-suicide-bombers-who-a6947311.html|title=Khalid and Brahim el-Bakraoui named as suicide bombers behind Brussels Airport attacks|work=Independent|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323091649/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-khalid-brahim-el-bakraoui-suicide-bombers-who-a6947311.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBCzh suspects"/>[[土耳其|土耳其]]当局在24日称曾于2015年6月在土耳其与[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]边境附近抓到易卜拉欣，怀疑他可能是前往叙利亚的伊斯兰国外国武装者。并将他遣返回荷兰，同时向比荷两国报告了这一情报。但当时比利时当局未能发现他与恐怖主义势力之间的联系，因此荷兰当局将他释放。<ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" />

当地媒体报道机场监控录像中显示的一名嫌疑人身份为1991年出生的纳吉姆·拉奇拉烏伊（{{lang|en|Najim Laachraoui}}）。拉奇拉烏伊出生于[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]，在比利时长大。警方认为机场发现的未爆炸的第三枚炸弹，也是三枚炸弹中威力最强的一枚，便是这一名嫌疑人留在现场的。警方此前已经于3月21日在巴黎恐袭案嫌疑人的房间中发现了他的DNA，还了解到他曾与阿卜杜勒－萨拉姆共同前往[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]，已经认定此人与巴黎恐袭相关，但一直未能成功抓获。<ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/><ref name="telegraph whois">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12201940/Brussels-attack-suspects-unmasked-the-El-Bakraoui-brothers.html|title=El Bakraoui brothers: Who are the suicide bombers Khalid and Brahim behind the Brussels attacks?|work=Telegraph|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-24|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323214215/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/belgium/12201940/Brussels-attack-suspects-unmasked-the-El-Bakraoui-brothers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBCzh suspects">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/03/160323_brussels_attacks_two_brothers|title=比利時連環爆炸：「兩兄弟」策劃了布魯塞爾機場爆炸案|work=BBC|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323172302/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2016/03/160323_brussels_attacks_two_brothers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-fugitive-in-airport-attack-named-as-chief-isis-bomb-maker-najim-laachraoui-a6947336.html|title=Brussels attacks: Fugitive named as 'chief Isis bomb maker' Najim Laachraoui|work=Independent|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323091534/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-fugitive-in-airport-attack-named-as-chief-isis-bomb-maker-najim-laachraoui-a6947336.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>3月23日上午，警方在比利时[[安德莱赫特|安德莱赫特]]逮捕了一名嫌疑人，但之后表示并非之前确定的第三位嫌疑人拉奇拉烏伊，认为他和其他数名嫌疑人仍然在逃。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-suspect-najim-laachraoui-arrested-in-anderlecht-a-day-after-isis-bombings-a6947506.html|title=Brussels attacks suspect Najim Laachraoui 'arrested in Anderlecht a day after Isis bombings|work=Independent|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323061914/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attacks-suspect-najim-laachraoui-arrested-in-anderlecht-a-day-after-isis-bombings-a6947506.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref name="Guardianlive23Mar16">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/mar/23/brussels-attacks-police-search-airport-bomb-suspect-live|title=Brussels attacks: live|work=The Guardian|date=2016-03-23|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323021812/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/mar/23/brussels-attacks-police-search-airport-bomb-suspect-live|dead-url=no}}</ref>24日，警方确认拉奇拉烏伊是机场的第二名自杀袭击者，已在袭击中身亡。警方还认为他还在这一系列爆炸案负责制作炸弹的工作，同时在巴黎袭击案中也扮演了重要角色。<ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/><ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="CNNlive22Mar16" /><ref name="CNN 6detained">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/24/europe/brussels-investigation/|title=6 detained in raids in Belgium|work=CNN|date=2016-03-24|accessdate=2016-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328153410/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/24/europe/brussels-investigation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

24日，警方确认地铁站的爆炸案中还有一名嫌疑人，并展开了追捕。<ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" />但其具体身份和状况均未知晓。而机场监控视频中的另一人身份不明，仍然在逃。在追捕行动中，警方逮捕了6名可能与案件相关的人员。<ref name="CNN 6detained"/>25日，比利时当局对前一日逮捕的费萨尔·C（{{lang|en|Faycal C.}}）提出指控，称其涉嫌“参与恐怖主义活动”以及“恐怖主义谋杀未遂”。警方称在其家中未搜获武器或炸药，但没有透露更多细节。<ref name="CNN Mar26"/>有媒体报道称其姓名为费萨尔·谢富（{{lang|en|Faycal Cheffou}}），认为他是机场监控视频中出现的第三位嫌疑人。<ref name="Guardian Mar26"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/brussels-attacks/brussels-bombings-prosecutors-issue-warrant-suspect-faycal-c-n545961|title=Brussels Bombings: Faycal Cheffou Faces Terror Charges|work=NBC News|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2019-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523002123/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/brussels-attacks/brussels-bombings-prosecutors-issue-warrant-suspect-faycal-c-n545961|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters faycalc">{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-belgium-blast-cheffou-idUKKCN0WS0C1|title=Belgium charges three men with terrorism after Brussels bombs|work=Reuters|date=2016-03-26|accessdate=2016-03-26|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327022725/http://uk.reuters.com/article/us-belgium-blast-cheffou-idUKKCN0WS0C1|dead-url=no}}</ref>但警方在3月29日因证据不足而将其释放。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attack-belgian-police-release-man-in-the-hat-suspect-faycal-c-citing-lack-of-evidence-a6956686.html|title=Brussels attack: Belgian police release 'man in the hat' suspect Faycal C citing lack of evidence|work=Independent|date=2016-03-29|accessdate=2016-03-30|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328192938/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/brussels-attack-belgian-police-release-man-in-the-hat-suspect-faycal-c-citing-lack-of-evidence-a6956686.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[德国|德国]]警方也逮捕了可能与此案相关的一名[[摩洛哥|摩洛哥]]人，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/25/europe/brussels-investigation/|title=Brussels attacks: Suspect wounded, arrested in police operation|work=CNN|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326220907/http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/25/europe/brussels-investigation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[意大利|意大利]]警方在26日亦逮捕了一名可能与布鲁塞尔和巴黎两次袭击有关的[[阿尔及利亚|阿尔及利亚]]人。<ref name="CNN Mar26"/>4月8日，比利时警方在布鲁塞尔附近逮捕了一名巴黎恐袭案的关键嫌疑人穆罕默德·阿布里尼（{{lang|en|Mohamed Abrini}}），阿布里尼随后在10日承认自己就是机场监控视频中出现的第三名嫌疑人。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/04/08/europe/brussels-attack-arrests/|title=Paris terror suspect Mohamed Abrini arrested in Belgium|work=CNN|date=2016-04-09|accessdate=2016-04-10|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411061036/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/04/08/europe/brussels-attack-arrests|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36000407|title=Paris attacks: Key suspect Abrini arrested in Brussels|work=BBC|date=2016-04-10|accessdate=2016-10-14|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410161348/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36000407|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Abrini">{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-belgium-blast-abrini-idUKKCN0X60PV|title=Paris suspect admits to being Brussels airport 'man in hat' - prosecutors|work=Reuters|date=2016-04-10|accessdate=2016-04-10|archive-date=2016-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160420081512/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-belgium-blast-abrini-idUKKCN0X60PV|dead-url=no}}</ref>

