机场袭击事件发生后，当局临时封闭了整座布鲁塞尔机场的空中交通，并疏散了机场内旅客。比利时政府将国内的警戒级别提高至最高。<ref name="GuardLive22Mar16">{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/mar/22/brussels-airport-explosions-live-updates|title=Brussells Airport explosions - live updates|author=Matthew Weaver|date=22 March 2016|work=The Guardian|accessdate=22 March 2016|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181432/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/mar/22/brussels-airport-explosions-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC initial report">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35869254|title=Brussels Zaventem airport rocked by two explosions|date=22 March 2016|work=BBC|accessdate=22 March 2016|archive-date=2017-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221210857/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-35869254|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BrusselsAirport |number=712182332623626240 |date=22 March 2016 |title=There have been 2 explosions at the airport. Building is being evacuated. Don't come to the airport area.}}</ref><ref>{{cite tweet |user=BrusselsAirport |number=712184823893331968 |date=22 March 2016 |title=Don't come to the airport - airport is being evacuated. Avoid the airport area. Flights have been cancelled.}}</ref>地铁站遭袭击后，包括[[布鲁塞尔地铁|布鲁塞尔地铁]]、有轨电车以及公共汽车在内的整个公交系统暂停运营，博物馆和大型商场也全部关闭，直至24日开始逐步恢复。政府呼吁市民留在家中，避免出门。地铁站附近的欧盟各部门总部进入封锁状态，所有会议取消。布鲁塞尔市内的[[布鲁塞尔南站|布鲁塞尔南站]]、[[布鲁塞尔北站|布鲁塞尔北站]]和[[布鲁塞尔中央车站|布鲁塞尔中央车站]]全部疏散人员暂停运营；南站和北站在下午4时重新开放。[[欧洲之星|欧洲之星]]暂停了[[布鲁塞尔南站|布鲁塞尔南站]]的所有列车服务；[[巴黎北站|巴黎北站]]与布鲁塞尔之间的[[大力士高速列车|国际列车]]也被全部取消，法国同时也取消了巴黎北站和伦敦之间的列车并封闭了法比两国之间的所有地面交通，巴黎北站也短暂关闭。<ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref name="telegraphlive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBClive22Mar16" />比利时境内的两座[[核电站|核电站]]中的非关键工作人员被疏散。<ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="CNNlive22Mar16"/>比利时警方在爆炸后搜查了可能的嫌疑人住所，在爆炸现场附近排查并引爆了可疑的包裹。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rtbf.be/info/societe/detail_explosions-a-zaventem-et-dans-le-metro-a-bruxelles-niveau-de-menace-a-4?id=9247721|title=Trois explosions à Bruxelles, des dizaines de morts: suivez toutes les infos en direct|work=rtbf|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|language=fr|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322172938/http://www.rtbf.be/info/societe/detail_explosions-a-zaventem-et-dans-le-metro-a-bruxelles-niveau-de-menace-a-4?id=9247721|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.tagesschau.de/ausland/explosion-am-flughafen-bruessel-105.html|title=Explosionen in Brüssel - was bisher bekannt ist|work=Tagesschau|date=2016-03-22|accessdate=2016-03-22|language=de|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322100655/http://www.tagesschau.de/ausland/explosion-am-flughafen-bruessel-105.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GuardLive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBClive22Mar16" /><ref name="BBCsofar"/>

